      "text": "Equation 4: Bucket × institution (Our core contribution)\n\nDo institutions condition the robot effect differently across\ndifferent types of industries?",
      "fontSize": 15.977330482483238,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Equation 4: Bucket × institution (Our core contribution)\n\nDo institutions condition the robot effect differently across different types of industries?",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3o85T3Rr0SLcntT64ZLUF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1284.7927464417853,
      "y": 4891.730166100997,
      "width": 498.15349641567985,
      "height": 40.76092045490402,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
